  "url": "https://www.tamilmirror.lk/\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd/\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd-\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd-\u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b95-\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8-\u0baa\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95-\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd/175-300329",
  "time_ut": 1657698361,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u2019\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'Don't sacrifice the country for Ranil's greed for office'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "National People's Shakti leader Anura Kumara Dissanayake said that the country and the countrymen should not be sacrificed for the greed of an individual named Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe and said that the government is trying to use the Anti-Terrorism Act to suppress the protesters.",
        "Continuing his address, he said that since the country has reached a decisive point, if the politicians and the public do not behave wisely, a worse situation will occur in the country.",
        "Especially today (13) the Speaker had announced that the President would resign. However, the resignation of the President was not officially announced until noon today. He said that the information available to us indicates that Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has been appointed as the Acting President.",
        "He also said that Ranil is using the power he has got to carry out repressions and to act in an undemocratic manner.",
        "According to this, the curfew has been enforced in the Upper Province. He also said that it is known that Ranil is trying to use the Anti-Terrorism Act against the protesters.",
        "Please listen to people's voice, people's aspirations and goals. Anurakumara Dissanayake said that the country and its people should not be sacrificed for the greed of individuals.",
        "Emergency Act has been implemented. It is an oppressive law. Army, Air Force and Navy should not listen to any orders to oppress the people regardless of the repressive needs of the government. The triad should stand on the side of the people. Do not use tear gas or water cannons against people. Similarly, he said, do not turn your weapons towards the people."
      ],
